headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Podium: The Nebula Turbo
content:
Stop by the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort anytime this week and give the Lucky Wheel a spin to walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, snacks, and all manner of mystery prizes.

This week on the podium? None other than the Nebula Turbo — a two-door sedan from the ’70s that has all the boxy, hard edges you’ve come to expect from a vintage European sports car. Let’s just say that if this car could talk, it’d have an accent thicker than oatmeal.
